  "text": [
    "They sap man\u2019s substance",
    "as moon the dew.",
    "A rope grows erect",
    "from the crown of the head.",
    "A black swan hatches",
    "from a pebble.",
    "And a flock of angels in the sky",
    "is taking an evening class",
    "on the skid pan.",
    "I dream, so I dream.",
    "I dream",
    "that three times three is nine,",
    "that the right-hand",
    "rule applies;",
    "and when the circus leaves",
    "the trampled ground will",
    "once more overgrow with grass.",
    "Yes, grass.",
    "Unequivocal grass.",
    "Just grass."
  ],
  "title": "Dreams",
  "year": ""
